    <section id="rn-401-intro"><title>Introduction</title>
<para>Globus Toolkit 4.0.1 is an incremental release of the Globus Toolkit containing updates to the 4.0.0 release.</para>
<para>This page only lists the fixes since 4.0.0; for release notes specific to 4.0.0 go to:
    <ulink url="http://www.globus.org/toolkit/releasenotes/4.0.0/">http://www.globus.org/toolkit/releasenotes/4.0.0/</ulink>.</para>
    <para>Use the existing documentation for 4.0, which starts at <ulink url="http://www.globus.org/toolkit/docs/4.0/">http://www.globus.org/toolkit/docs/4.0/</ulink>.</para>
        </section>
